column2: SELECT   d.*,    s.specObjID, s.zWarning, s.class       FROM MyDB.LAMOS_dr6_radec1 AS d   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjAllEq( d.ra_obs, d.dec_obs, #) AS n    INNER JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.specObjID = s.specObjID                     INTO MyDB.LAMOST1_dr6_DR1# ORDER BY d.obsid, n.distance
